## 🎮 Core Systems (No Trait System)

### ❌ EXCLUDED
- Trait Mastery System (마스터리) - All 5 types removed
- Trait Points - No automatic bonus distribution
- Character Stat Point Distribution - Automatic only

### ✅ INCLUDED (4 Systems)

#### 1. Card System (200 types)
- Types: ATTACK (42) / SKILL (60) / POWER (50) / CURSE (48)
- Rarity: COMMON 40% → RARE 35% → SPECIAL 15% → LEGENDARY 10%
- Enhancement: Same card ×2 (or + Gold)
- Success Rate: 100%
- Max Level: +10 (auto stop)
- Reference: CARD_200_DETAILED_DESIGN_GUIDE.md

#### 2. Equipment Enhancement (66 items, 4 slots)
- Slots: Weapon / Armor / Accessory / Off-Hand
- Enhancement: Same equipment ×2 + Gold
- Success Rate: 100% (no failures)
- Max Level: +10
- P2W Ratio: 1.86x (target: 1.5x)
- Reference: CHARACTER_EQUIPMENT_SYSTEM.md

#### 3. Progression System (Infinite Levels)
- Level Range: Lv 1 ~ 1000+ (endless)
- EXP Formula: 100 × (current_level ^ 1.2)
- Auto Stat Distribution (NO player choice):
  * ATK: +1.5 per level
  * DEF: +1 per level
  * HP: +5 per level
  * SPD: +0.3 per level
- Milestone Rewards (Currency + Content Unlock):
  * Early (Lv 1-20): Every 2 levels
  * Mid (Lv 21-50): Every 5 levels
  * Late (Lv 51+): Increasing intervals
- Reference: PROGRESSION_SYSTEM_REDESIGNED.md

#### 4. Gacha System
- Types: Equipment Gacha (50D) + Card Gacha (50D)
- Drop Rates:
  * Equipment: 55% COMMON, 30% RARE, 13% SPECIAL, 2% LEGENDARY
  * Cards: 45% COMMON, 35% RARE, 15% SPECIAL, 5% LEGENDARY
- Guarantee: 50-pull (RARE) / 100-pull (SPECIAL) / 150-pull (LEGENDARY)
- Reference: GACHA_ENHANCEMENT_FINAL_SIMPLIFIED.md

